name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $::type
desc: Returns: Identifier for a family of the event.  For example, a menu item, program, rule, policy, function code, application name or URL. It identifies the performed function.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifier for a family of the event.  For example, a menu item, program, rule, policy, function code, application name or URL. It identifies the performed function.

name: $subtype
desc: Returns: Identifier for the category of event.

name: $addsubtype
desc: Identifier for the category of event.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Identifier for the category of event.

name: $action
desc: Returns: Indicator for type of action performed during the event that generated the audit.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicator for type of action performed during the event that generated the audit.

name: $severity
desc: Returns: Indicates and enables segmentation of various severity including debugging from critical.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates and enables segmentation of various severity including debugging from critical.

name: $period
desc: Returns: The period during which the activity occurred.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The period during which the activity occurred.

name: $recorded
desc: Returns: The time when the event was recorded.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The time when the event was recorded.

name: $outcome
desc: Returns: Indicates whether the event succeeded or failed.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates whether the event succeeded or failed.

name: $outcomeDesc
desc: Returns: A free text description of the outcome of the event.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A free text description of the outcome of the event.

name: $purposeOfEvent

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The purposeOfUse (reason) that was used during the event being recorded.

desc: An actor taking an active role in the event or activity that is logged.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: An actor taking an active role in the event or activity that is logged.

name: $source
desc: Returns: The system that is reporting the event.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The system that is reporting the event.
